						<div class="postbody">To compare large numbers, try using cmp for the first and sbc for the rest.<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; lda this_lo<br />&nbsp; cmp that_lo&nbsp; &nbsp;; set up carry for next sbc<br />&nbsp; lda this_hi<br />&nbsp; sbc that_hi<br />&nbsp; ; right now, carry is set if and only if this &gt;= that<br /></div></div>

