 &nbsp; ;I also understand these... cameraposition = 0<br />sta camerapositionhigh<br />sta camperapositionlow<br /><br />abovezero:<br />;Can be optimized in cute ways... ^_^<br /></div><br /><br />edit: Well... I looked at this some more and want to say that I notice you aren't using <strong>sec</strong> before my first question line... so that 128 would be the low... and 00 would be the high...  I still don't understand, I'm thinking... but Yes I dont understand.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_redface.gif" alt=":oops:" title="Embarassed" /></div>

